text: Milan Hilderink (born 29 September 2002) is a Dutch professional football player who plays as a Defender and he is currently playing for the Dutch Eerste Divisie side, De Graafschap. ==Club career== In 2019 summer transfer window, he signed a 2 years' length contract with De Graafschap's senior team. He made his professional debut on 23 August 2019 in the match against FC Volendam after replacing Gregor Breinburg in the 83th minute. ==References== Category:Living people Category:2002 births Category:Footballers from Gelderland Category:Association football defenders Category:Eerste Divisie players Category:De Graafschap players Category:Dutch footballers
